--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VENDORED / UPSTREAM ENGINE COMPONENTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Browser 2030B integrates upstream browser engines (Chromium/Blink and
Gecko/SpiderMonkey) as VENDORED components under engine/ (fetched by
./bootstrap; not committed to this repository). Those components remain under
their OWN original licenses (e.g. BSD-3-Clause, MPL-2.0, LGPL, and others as
documented by each upstream project). This project does NOT relicense them.

When such vendored components are combined with this Work and distributed as a
whole (a "Larger Work" under §B.4), the combined distribution preserves the
Ethical-Use Conditions of Part C as the ethical floor (§B.5). The upstream
components keep their own license terms for their own files. See
docs/10-licensing-and-ethics.md for the per-dependency compatibility analysis.

